Banking & Finance Partner, Dubai
Banking & Finance Partner, Dubai
Location:  --Dubai
Our client is a rated boutique law firm with a regional footprint. The firm’s highly experienced partners have backgrounds with lea dining international law firms and have collectively developed a very high quality corporate client base which includes investment banks, private equity houses, funds, and regional corporates.
The Firm is now looking to expand the team further with the hire of a dynamic banking & finance partner. Candidates should have established relationships with financial institutions in the region and be keen to work with a smaller firm that has ambitious plans to continue to develop as a force in the market. The firm receives high-level instructions, often competing successfully for mandates up against leading UK law firms, and US and is highly profitable.
